{
  "meta": {
    "title": "Shionverse Skit 011",
    "description": "Talking about tarot — how cards, hearts, and the starrealm quietly connect.",
    "version": "1.0"
  },
  "start": "intro",
  "nodes": {
    "intro": {
      "id": "intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shiopon",
      "text": "ねえねえ、シオンさん。タロットってさ、どうして星と似てる感じがするの〜？",
      "next": "shion_reply",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "calm-smile", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "listening", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "thinking", "speaking": true }
      ]
    },

    "shion_reply": {
      "id": "shion_reply",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shion",
      "text": "ああ……それはね。タロットも、星も、直接答えをくれるわけじゃないからだと思う。",
      "next": "lumiere_add",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "thoughtful", "speaking": true },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "listening", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "warm", "speaking": false }
      ]
    },

    "lumiere_add": {
      "id": "lumiere_add",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "lumiere",
      "text": "はい、シオン様のおっしゃる通りでございます。タロットは未来を決めるものではなく、心がどこを向いているかを映す鏡のようなものです。",
      "next": "shiopon_react",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "patient", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "soft-smile", "speaking": true },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "thinking", "speaking": false }
      ]
    },

    "shiopon_react": {
      "id": "shiopon_react",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shiopon",
      "text": "えっ、じゃあ当たるとか外れるとかじゃないの？",
      "next": "shion_smile",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "surprised", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "wondering", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "excited", "speaking": true }
      ]
    },

    "shion_smile": {
      "id": "shion_smile",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shion",
      "text": "はは。そこも大事だけどね。でも本当は、カードを見た時に『あ、分かる』って思う気持ちの方が近い。",
      "next": "lumiere_star",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "gentle", "speaking": true },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "listening", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "warm", "speaking": false }
      ]
    },

    "lumiere_star": {
      "id": "lumiere_star",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "lumiere",
      "text": "星界では、その『分かる』という感覚を、セレフィーズ達の心の響きと呼びます。タロットは、その声が届く小さな扉でございます。",
      "next": "shiopon_understand",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "patient", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "inspired", "speaking": true },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "thinking", "speaking": false }
      ]
    },

    "shiopon_understand": {
      "id": "shiopon_understand",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shiopon",
      "text": "そっか……。じゃあタロットって、星界のみんなとお話しするみたいなものなんだね。",
      "next": "shion_relief",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "relief", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "soft-smile", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "warm", "speaking": true }
      ]
    },

    "shion_relief": {
      "id": "shion_relief",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shion",
      "text": "うん。だから怖がらなくていいし、無理に信じなくてもいい。ただ、そっと耳を澄ませばいい。",
      "next": "ending",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "calm-smile", "speaking": true },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "grateful", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "warm", "speaking": false }
      ]
    },

    "ending": {
      "id": "ending",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "shiopon",
      "text": "えへへ……それなら、しおぽんもタロット好き！なんだか、やさしい感じがするもん。",
      "cast": [
        { "slot": "left", "character": "shion", "expression": "smiling", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "center", "character": "lumiere", "expression": "soft-smile", "speaking": false },
        { "slot": "right", "character": "shiopon", "expression": "cheerful", "speaking": true }
      ]
    }
  }
}
